<div class="wp-block-group alignwide is-style-faq"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"><h3 class="wp-block-heading">
				Ofte stilte spørsmål
			</h3><div class="t2-accordion wp-block-t2-accordion" data-allow-multiple="1" role="list"><div class="t2-accordion-item wp-block-t2-accordion-item" role="listitem">
			<h2 class="t2-accordion-title">
				<button type="button" class="t2-accordion-trigger" id="kan-man-overnatte-i-en-dagsturhytte?" aria-controls="accordion-panel" aria-expanded="false">
					Kan man overnatte i en dagsturhytte?
					<span class="t2-accordion-icon is-closed-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="24" width="24" class="t2-icon t2-icon-chevrondown" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M12 14.9c-.1 0-.3 0-.4-.1-.1 0-.2-.1-.3-.2L6.7 10c-.2-.1-.3-.4-.3-.6 0-.3.1-.5.3-.7.2-.2.4-.3.7-.3s.5.1.7.3l3.9 3.9 3.9-3.9c.2-.2.4-.3.7-.3.3 0 .5.1.7.3.2.2.3.4.3.7s-.1.5-.3.7l-4.6 4.6c-.1.1-.2.2-.3.2H12z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span>
					<span class="t2-accordion-icon is-open-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="24" width="24" class="t2-icon t2-icon-chevronup" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M6.7 14.7c-.2-.2-.3-.4-.3-.7s.1-.5.3-.7l4.6-4.6c.1-.1.2-.2.3-.2.1 0 .2-.1.4-.1.1 0 .3 0 .4.1.1 0 .2.1.3.2l4.6 4.6c.2.2.3.4.3.7s-.1.5-.3.7c-.2.2-.4.3-.7.3s-.5-.1-.7-.3L12 10.8l-3.9 3.9c-.2.2-.4.3-.7.3s-.5-.1-.7-.3z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span>
				</button>
			</h2>
			<div class="t2-accordion-item__inner-container is-layout-flow" id="accordion-panel" aria-labelledby="kan-man-overnatte-i-en-dagsturhytte?" role="region" hidden>
				<p class="">
				Dagsturhytter er for alle, og du kan ikke oppføre deg sånn at andre ikke kan bruke hytta. Magnus dro opp senhøstes, og var alene der. Om du legger deg i sovepose i en dagsturhytte eller gapahuk, har andre selvsagt lov til å gjøre det samme. 
			</p>
			</div>
		</div><div class="t2-accordion-item wp-block-t2-accordion-item" role="listitem">
			<h2 class="t2-accordion-title">
				<button type="button" class="t2-accordion-trigger" id="er-dette-en-lett-tur?" aria-controls="accordion-panel-1" aria-expanded="false">
					Er dette en lett tur?
					<span class="t2-accordion-icon is-closed-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="24" width="24" class="t2-icon t2-icon-chevrondown" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M12 14.9c-.1 0-.3 0-.4-.1-.1 0-.2-.1-.3-.2L6.7 10c-.2-.1-.3-.4-.3-.6 0-.3.1-.5.3-.7.2-.2.4-.3.7-.3s.5.1.7.3l3.9 3.9 3.9-3.9c.2-.2.4-.3.7-.3.3 0 .5.1.7.3.2.2.3.4.3.7s-.1.5-.3.7l-4.6 4.6c-.1.1-.2.2-.3.2H12z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span>
